						<p>Gift of 6 <hi rend="italic">mā</hi> of tax-free land by Tāyaṉ Kaṇamuḍaiyāṉ for a lamp to the temple of Mahādēva on the hill at Śrīkaṇṭha-chaturvēdimaṅgalam, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> on the southern bank.</p>						

